sequenceDiagram
%% OTT Zapping v2 (open source)
%%   GORE (ExoPlayer/Media3 javni API) = implementation-level, konkretni pozivi, hronoloski timeline
%%   DOLE (ispod plejera)               = PDF sablon Platforme/HAL (demonstration, BEZ konkretnih poziva)
%% Open-source plejer = ExoPlayer (androidx.media3). Nema Comedia, nema tunera - IP izvor (HLS/DASH).
%% Sabloni: Module 5 Fig.3, Module 6 Fig.5 (A/V playback), Module 3 (PTS), Module 7 (OTT preko HTTP/TCP)
%% --- Android open source dokumentacija (verifikovano) ---
%% ExoPlayer (start):  https://developer.android.com/media/media3/exoplayer/hello-world
%% Player.Listener:    https://developer.android.com/media/media3/exoplayer/listening-to-player-events
%% HLS:                https://developer.android.com/media/media3/exoplayer/hls
%% DASH:               https://developer.android.com/media/media3/exoplayer/dash
%% Media sources/ABR:  https://developer.android.com/media/media3/exoplayer/media-sources
%% TV Input Framework: https://developer.android.com/training/tv/tif/ui
%% Media3 izvor (Apache-2.0): https://github.com/androidx/media
  autonumber
  actor User
  box rgb(235,245,255) Android app
    participant App as Live TV App
    participant TIS as OTT TvInputService
  end
  box rgb(232,245,233) Open-source player - ExoPlayer / AndroidX Media3
    participant PLAYER as ExoPlayer
    participant SRC as HLS/DASH MediaSource
  end
  box rgb(255,243,224) Ispod plejera - Platform i HAL - demonstration
    participant NET as HTTP/TCP + TLS -> Network HAL
    participant AVDEC as MediaCodec / AudioTrack
  end

  User->>App: Play OTT channel
  App->>TIS: onSetSurface(surface)
  App->>TIS: onSetStreamVolume(0.0)
  App->>TIS: onTune(channelUri)
  Note over TIS: channelUri -> stream URL iz TV Provider-a<br/>(internalProviderData, npr. https://.../stream.m3u8)
  TIS->>App: notifyVideoUnavailable(VIDEO_UNAVAILABLE_REASON_TUNING)
  TIS->>PLAYER: new ExoPlayer.Builder(context).build()
  TIS->>PLAYER: setVideoSurface(surface)
  TIS->>PLAYER: setVolume(0.0f)
  Note over PLAYER: Media3 javni API: onSetSurface->setVideoSurface(Surface),<br/>onSetStreamVolume(0.0)->setVolume(0.0f) (mute); TIF doc prikazuje stari createMessage(renderer) obrazac
  TIS->>PLAYER: addListener(playerListener)
  TIS->>PLAYER: setMediaItem(MediaItem.fromUri(streamUrl))
  Note over PLAYER,SRC: DefaultMediaSourceFactory bira HLS (.m3u8) / DASH (.mpd) / Progressive po URL/MIME
  TIS->>PLAYER: prepare()
  Note over PLAYER,SRC: prepare() je ASINHRON; manifest + segmenti se ucitavaju (STATE_BUFFERING -> STATE_READY)

  PLAYER->>SRC: ucitaj manifest (HLS/DASH) + segmente
  SRC->>NET: HTTP GET manifest + media segmenti (TLS); ABR bira bitrate
  Note over NET: demonstration: TCP/TLS preko Network HAL (Wi-Fi/Ethernet)<br/>nema tunera/demuksa - OTT je IP izvor
  NET-->>SRC: segmenti (fMP4 / TS)
  SRC-->>PLAYER: track-ovi (video/audio/text) + PTS timeline
  PLAYER->>AVDEC: dekoduj video (MediaCodec) + audio (AudioTrack); A/V sync po PTS
  Note over AVDEC: demonstration: video+audio dekoder + display<br/>komunicira sa HAL (VDEC/ADEC/GPU) (ref. Module 6 Fig.5)
  AVDEC-->>PLAYER: A/V tece, sinhronizovano

  TIS->>PLAYER: play() (setPlayWhenReady(true))
  PLAYER-->>TIS: Player.Listener.onPlaybackStateChanged(STATE_READY)
  PLAYER-->>TIS: Player.Listener.onRenderedFirstFrame()
  TIS->>PLAYER: setVolume(volume) (unmute - restore)
  TIS->>App: notifyVideoAvailable()
  TIS->>PLAYER: getCurrentTracks() -> notifyTracksChanged(List<TvTrackInfo>)
  PLAYER-->>TIS: Tracks (video/audio/text)
  TIS-->>App: Service started -> Playback active
